description:
LoggedMdt:  Table containing logged MDT (Mobile Data Transmission) configuration and status information from Ericsson RAN.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the log entry.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area (e.g., cell site location).
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely redundant).
- Id4: Unknown identifier (likely redundant).
- vsDataType: Type of data logged (specific to Ericsson).
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- LoggedMdt.traceId: Trace identifier.
- LoggedMdt.tceId: TCE (Trace Collection Element) identifier.
- LoggedMdt.traceRecSessionReference: Session reference for the trace recording.
- LoggedMdt.areaScopeCgiList: List of Cell Global Identifiers (CGIs) defining the area scope.
- LoggedMdt.loggedMdtGnssCheck: Boolean indicating if GNSS check is enabled for MDT.
- LoggedMdt.loggedMdtId: Unique identifier for the MDT configuration.
- LoggedMdt.loggingInterval: Logging interval duration.
- LoggedMdt.loggedMdtReportEnabled: Boolean indicating if MDT reporting is enabled.
- LoggedMdt.loggedMdtConfigEnabled: Boolean indicating if MDT configuration is enabled.
- LoggedMdt.numberOfMdtConfigUes: Number of UEs configured for MDT.
- LoggedMdt.loggingDuration: Duration of the MDT logging session.
- LoggedMdt.mdtPlmnList: List of PLMNs (Public Land Mobile Networks) for MDT.
- LoggedMdt.areaScopeType: Type of area scope used for MDT.
- LoggedMdt.areaScopeTacList: List of Tracking Area Codes (TACs) defining the area scope.
